 נניח כי
\begin_inset Formula $w\in\stackrel[k\neq i]{}{\sum}ImP_{k}$
\end_inset

, אזי 
\begin_inset Formula $w\in\stackrel[k\neq i]{}{\sum}ImP_{k}\Rightarrow w=\stackrel[i\neq k]{}{\sum}w_{k}$
